nodes.text: The Rusty Freighter Cantina was a cantina in the Entertainment Plaza district of Corellia's Blastfield Shipyards. During the Battle of Corellia, a group of Mandalorians cornered the Nautolan Jedi Bengel Morr in the cantina, though he was saved by the timely arrival of the Jedi Knight known as the Hero of Tython.
